                "category": "defensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>Whenever the drakauthix takes at least 10 slashing damage, it releases a cloud of brown spores in a @Template[emanation|distance:20] that persists for 1 minute (or until dispersed by a strong wind). All creatures within the spores become @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Concealed], and all creatures outside the spores become concealed to creatures within it. Within this cloud of spores, the drakauthix's sporesight becomes a precise sense. The spore cloud does not move with the drakauthix nor is it displaced by its movement.</p>"
